tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE shipments (
    shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
    arrival_date DATE,
    quantity INT,
    shipment_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE quality_checks (
    check_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    shipment_id INT,
    check_date DATE,
    passed BOOLEAN,
    reason VARCHAR(255),
    FOREIGN KEY (shipment_id) REFERENCES shipments(shipment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE shipment_products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    shipment_id UUID,
    product_name VARCHAR(100),
    quantity INT,
    expiration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE quality_checks (
    check_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    shipment_id INT REFERENCES shipments(shipment_id),
    check_type TEXT,
    check_result TEXT,
    check_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    check_id INT REFERENCES quality_checks(check_id),
    inspector_id INT REFERENCES inspectors(inspector_id),
    report_details TEXT,
    report_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE shipments (
    shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_name VARCHAR,
    product_name VARCHAR,
    quantity INT,
    arrival_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE quality_checks (
    check_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    shipment_id INT,
    check_date DATE,
    pass_status BOOLEAN,
    remarks TEXT
);
